		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You sling a blast of unstable, coruscating energy at your target, subjecting it to unknown&mdash;but always unpleasant&mdash;effects.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Make a ranged spell attack against your target, on a hit, the target takes 4d6 damage and suffers an additional effect until the end of your next turn. Roll on the table below to determine the type of damage and corresponding effect.</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"51\"><col width=\"573\"></colgroup>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1d10</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Damage and Effect</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Radiant, and the target is outlined in a faerie fire effect until the end of its next turn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Necrotic, and the target suffers disadvantage on Perception checks until the end of its next turn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Poison, and the target suffers the poisoned condition until the end of its next turn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Fire, and the target takes 1d4 ongoing fire damage for one minute or until an action is used to extinguish the flames</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Cold, and the target&rsquo;s move speeds are reduced by 10 feet until the end of its next turn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Lightning, and the target has disadvantage on Dextertity checks and saves until the end of its next turn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Thunder, and the target is deafened until the end of its next turn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Acid, and the target is rattled until the end of its next turn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">9</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Psychic, and the target is confused until the end of its next turn</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">10</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Force, and the target is knocked prone&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
